data.feature:
• Stretchy, Breathable, Weather-Resistant Fabric

    100% polyester (87% recycled) plain-weave shell and lining fabric offers generous mechanical stretch, exceptional breathability and improved abrasion resistance; microtexture creates excellent next-to-skin comfort; features a DWR (durable water repellent) finish

  • Revolutionary FullRange Insulation

    Revolutionary 60-g FullRangeÂ® insulation (40% recycled) warms and stretches and, combined with the shell and lining, supplies outstanding mechanical stretch and unprecedented air permeability (40CFM), allowing excess heat to move away from the body

  • Designed for Freedom of Movement

    Stretch fabrics and insulation, articulated patterning, and strategically placed, low-profile quilting provide exceptional range of motion for unhindered movement

  • Stretchy Hood

    Stretchy hood with binding easily pulls on or off, even when jacket is zipped

  • Center-Front Zipper

    Center-front zipper has zipper garage at chin for next-to-skin comfort

  • Pocket Features

    Two handwarmer pockets and a left-chest pocket are zippered, low-profile and low-bulk to wear comfortably with a harness or pack; self-stuffs into left-chest pocket

  • Low-Profile Variable Conditions Cuffs

    Sleek, low-bulk, snag-resistant Variable Conditions Cuffs use stretch knit for versatile coverage and comfort; elasticized hem seals in warmth; Fair Trade Certifiedâ¢ sewn

  • Country of Origin

    Made in Vietnam.

  • Weight

    346 g (12.2 oz)
